From 1ade25cf53bf29e49102ee06448104331b92e0e3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ibrahim Salman <ibrahim@portfolio-fix>
Date: Mon, 16 Mar 2026 17:29:50 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: complete 47-bug audit
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

SECURITY
- Delete deploy.js (POSTed project tarball to unknown server)
- Delete final_final_deploy_output.txt (exposed full Windows path + UET OneDrive username)
- Update .gitignore to block *.tgz, *_output.txt, deploy.js permanently

IDENTITY / CONTENT
- layout.tsx: title changed from 'Senior Frontend Architect' to 'Software Engineer'
- layout.tsx: OG/Twitter URLs fixed from staging deployment URL to relative paths
- ConsoleBreadcrumb: console log no longer claims fabricated seniority
- Hero.tsx: subtitle updated to honest student identity
- About.tsx: bio copy reflects real background (UET, IJT, actual projects)
- Skills.tsx: percentages corrected to honest student-level values
- Projects.tsx: replace 3 fictional projects with real ones (Dawn Scraper, BLAST, Portfolio)
- StatsRow.tsx: stat values replaced with honest numbers

DEAD CODE REMOVED
- Hero.tsx: removed unused FuzzyText import
- About.tsx: removed unused cn import, removed unused delay prop + default
- Contact.tsx: removed unused cn import
- AvailabilityBadge.tsx: cn was already unused (no change needed, existing code fine)
- SkillCard.tsx: removed empty useEffect(() => {}, [])
- ProjectCard.tsx: removed dead cardRef (was never attached to JSX)
- DebugPanel.tsx: removed orphaned useFrame + useRef imports after export statement
- FloatingModel.tsx: removed non-functional castShadow/receiveShadow props
- useMagneticEffect.ts: documented as utility hook (not orphaned, intentional)

FUNCTIONAL BUGS FIXED
- Contact.tsx: send command now performs real async fetch to Formspree instead of
  fake setTimeout simulation with hardcoded 200 OK response
- Contact.tsx: GitHub link fixed from non-existent profile to real devhms URL
- Hero.tsx: 'View my work' changed from dead <button> to <a href='#projects'>
- Hero.tsx: 'Download CV' changed from dead <button> to <a href='/cv.pdf'>
- ProjectCard.tsx: cards now render as <a> when link prop is provided; ArrowUpRight
  icon only shows when link exists
- StatsRow.tsx: spring config fixed (tension:20/friction:10 was critically
  underdamped causing oscillation); new values: tension:80/friction:30
- StatsRow.tsx: IntersectionObserver rootMargin '-100px' replaced with
  threshold:0.2 — fixes counters staying at 0 on smaller screens

CSS / STYLE BUGS FIXED
- globals.css: removed invalid --scroll-behavior CSS variable (not a real property)
- globals.css: added missing .underline-effect class (was used in Hero, never defined)
- globals.css: added missing .custom-scrollbar class (used in Contact + DebugPanel)
- FuzzyText.tsx: fixed SVG filter ID collision — now uses useId() for unique IDs
- FuzzyText.tsx: Tailwind font classes on SVG <text> replaced with inline style
  (Tailwind classes do not apply to SVG elements)
- CustomCursor.tsx: fixed cursor flash at (0,0) on load — initial position set
  to (-100,-100) off-screen, snaps to real position on first mousemove
- CustomCursor.tsx: scale transition fixed — transform added to transition list
- MagnetLines.tsx: lines no longer point to (0,0) before first mousemove
- MagnetLines.tsx: RAF loop now pauses via IntersectionObserver when off-screen
- MagnetLines.tsx: removed duplicate local cn() function, now imports from utils

TYPESCRIPT
- gsap.ts: removed @ts-nocheck suppression
- gsap.ts: ScrollTrigger registration deduplicated (was registered in both gsap.ts
  and lenis.ts)

PROJECT HYGIENE
- package.json: renamed from 'portfolio2' to 'ibrahim-salman-portfolio'
- package.json: critters moved from dependencies to devDependencies
- next.config.mjs: removed unstable experimental.optimizeCss (known build failures)
- layout.tsx: removed redundant <link rel=preconnect> (next/font handles this)
- layout.tsx: DM_Sans now loads weight 400 in addition to 300 and 500
- lenis.ts: rewritten from module-level singleton to initLenis()/destroyLenis()
  functions — fixes permanent smooth scroll breakage after component unmount
- SmoothScroll.tsx: updated to use new initLenis/destroyLenis API
- useTypewriter.ts: onComplete stabilised via ref pattern — fixes restart loop
  when caller passes inline arrow function
